Setup for project:

json server :
npm install -g json-server
start server: json-server --watch db.json

tailwindcss setup :
npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/cli
@import "tailwindcss";
npx @tailwindcss/cli -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch


package.json : 
 "scripts": {
    "dev": "npx @tailwindcss/cli -i ./src/css/input.css -o ./src/css/output.css --watch & json-server --watch db.json --port 8000"
  }


run project : npm run dev

